- Read the prisme-ai-docs MCP for high level documentation, and use the one from prisme-ai-builder when building YAML (DSUL) automation or pages.
- Always run a lint check using the prisme-ai-builder tool for this after creating or updating automations.
- Develop the automation in local, then ask the user for a review before you can push them to prisme.ai
- Run the automations you update on prisme.ai with test data to ensure it work properly, but always ask first.
- When installing an App, add it in the `imports` folder.